            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I cannot reproduce the issue in `NVIM v0.8.0-dev+580-g45ba2e147f7b`. The cursor and terminal buffer in my case remains as Suida expects.\r\n\r\nBy the way, @Suida , you should check `:h shell-powershell` and use those config as pwsh requires some extra tailoring to work properly. (To be clear, even Suida's repro of setting only `set shell=pwsh.exe\\ -nop` didn't reproduce the issue for me. The pwsh doc reference is just a by-the-by.)\r\n\r\nAlso, could you try and see if you can reproduce it in the old Windows conhost terminal?",
